  "1739650": {
    "name": "维度之间：无畏战舰设计师",
    "steam_appid": 1739650,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<strong><u>设计</u><br>用丰富的模块设计你的太空战舰。每一个模块都具有独特的属性和功能，你要以明确的策略去设计你的飞船，平衡机动性、持久性、火力、货仓空间、电力供应等各个方面。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2c06fe21ce06208dd2deff94d5e13f66.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2c06fe21ce06208dd2deff94d5e13f66.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2c06fe21ce06208dd2deff94d5e13f66.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>自定义</u><br>你可以完全自由的控制模块的三维尺寸，为每一个模块配置自定义颜色。注意模块的尺寸会影响其属性参数。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/592ebe44c753479ad222de758e9b3db2.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/592ebe44c753479ad222de758e9b3db2.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/592ebe44c753479ad222de758e9b3db2.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>指挥</u><br>你需要用策略指挥你的舰船，根据战场态势设定全舰战术策略。例如设定航行方向和航行姿态，更改炮塔攻击策略，安排能源供给优先级，甚至是使用独特技能扭转战场形势。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/db2a55d3862d898f1770a5e802a02600.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/db2a55d3862d898f1770a5e802a02600.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/db2a55d3862d898f1770a5e802a02600.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>物理模拟</u><br>游戏拥有拟真度极高的物理系统。如果舰船的关键模块节点被击毁，舰船的结构会断裂。推进器的推力和转向力矩是完全独立计算，放置位置和方向直接决定了飞船的加速和机动性能。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/02dad2b3ddd9ddcaeb0ccc1e1c62198c.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/02dad2b3ddd9ddcaeb0ccc1e1c62198c.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/02dad2b3ddd9ddcaeb0ccc1e1c62198c.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>开始一场冒险</u><br>选择一艘初始战船，在浩渺的星河中驰骋，赢得一次次战斗的胜利，不断升级强化自己的战舰。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2f46b09512ba846147ec6ae74764376d.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=616 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2f46b09512ba846147ec6ae74764376d.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/2f46b09512ba846147ec6ae74764376d.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>与好友联机</u><br>可以邀请你的好友来一场欢乐的局域网对战，可以一起对抗AI敌人，或者来一场公平竞赛，试试谁的战舰才是更强设计！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/7b17aa20b3b51c3b452adbc6723190a0.poster.avif?t=1737090752\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/7b17aa20b3b51c3b452adbc6723190a0.webm?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1739650/extras/7b17aa20b3b51c3b452adbc6723190a0.mp4?t=1737090752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong>",
